snippet.title: Carpocalypse Trailer
snippet.description:
A nuclear war wiped out most of humanity and created a toxic and radioactive cloud that kills everything it touches. Get in your car and drive as fast as you can and maybe you will live a little bit longer than the rest of humankind.

I made this game with a colleague for a university project/exam back in 2017.

The game: https://solobytegames.itch.io/carpocalypse

Twitter: https://twitter.com/SoloByteGames

SoloByteGames Itch.io: https://solobytegames.itch.io/
